data.description: Home located in the equestrian friendly section of Davie and on a Quiet Cul-de-Sac. Sale includes an adjacent lot with "Folio # 5040-22-02-0740", both lots equaling over 1 acre of land. Plenty of outdoor space for a pool, horses stall, and much more. Workshop that can easily be turned into an in-laws quarter. No HOA. A must-see It won’t last!!!
